title: DDFP 394: Week 5 review & Power Rankings
itunes:title: DDFP 394: Week 5 review & Power Rankings
description:
Shek is joined by Ike Taylor to discuss Monday Night Football, as well as his top five cornerbacks in the NFL. Later, Handsome Hank returns from London and joins the group with Maurice Jones-Drew to review Week 5. Lastly, Dan Hanzus and Gregg Rosenthal stop by to discuss their power rankings of the remaining undefeated teams.
